(Gu Huaijin)

00:37:05.159 --> 00:37:06.320
Can you

00:37:06.440 --> 00:37:07.480
be calm for a moment?

00:37:08.800 --> 00:37:10.400
I'm quite calm.

00:37:10.480 --> 00:37:12.199
I'm calmly
listening to you play the zither

00:37:12.599 --> 00:37:14.119
and calmly practicing my swordsmanship.

00:37:14.120 --> 00:37:16.230
Your father asked me
to teach you how to play zither

00:37:16.280 --> 00:37:18.800
just to calm your temper

00:37:19.039 --> 00:37:19.800
and be elegant.

00:37:20.440 --> 00:37:21.960
My father asked you to teach me these

00:37:22.199 --> 00:37:24.199
for noble reasons

00:37:24.400 --> 00:37:25.360
but in truth,

00:37:25.960 --> 00:37:28.719
he just wants
to raise an obedient sheep.

00:37:29.310 --> 00:37:30.639
When I'm at the age of marriage,

00:37:30.646 --> 00:37:33.320
he will marry me to a good family
to serve other people's parents,

00:37:33.320 --> 00:37:34.639
my husband and teach my children.

00:37:35.679 --> 00:37:36.920
But that's not what I want.

00:37:37.030 --> 00:37:38.880
I don't want to become
an obedient livestock.

00:37:39.920 --> 00:37:40.960
What do you want?

00:37:43.800 --> 00:37:46.199
I want to become a fit eagle

00:37:46.199 --> 00:37:47.400
to roam the martial world.

00:37:47.790 --> 00:37:49.360
I don't want to become somebody's wife.

00:37:59.800 --> 00:38:00.440
Pu Jingtang,

00:38:00.860 --> 00:38:02.679
