for the most noble family in Cangzhou.

00:39:29.760 --> 00:39:31.039
Unlike me.

00:39:32.239 --> 00:39:32.719
Bingyu,

00:39:32.840 --> 00:39:34.079
I'm already familiar

00:39:34.079 --> 00:39:35.790
